verbose_text: Haplotype base composition of the two plasmids suggests that this result may be produced by NG_012836.1 : g.4160T> C. NG_012836.1 : g.4160T> C is a tag SNP in which the C allele has been linked to the development of multiple psychiatric disorders, such as CAE (Tanaka et al., 2008) and heroin dependence (Chen et al., 2014).
evidence: result may be produced by NG_012836.1
